&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\"/></div></div><p class=\"text-[0.6rem] tracking-[0.5em] uppercase text-white/40 mb-3\" style=\"font-family:&#x27;Inter&#x27;, sans-serif;opacity:0;transform:translateY(8px)\">Welcome to</p><h1 class=\"text-white text-5xl sm:text-6xl font-bold tracking-tight leading-none mb-2\" style=\"font-family:&#x27;Playfair Display&#x27;, serif;opacity:0;transform:translateY(16px)\">SuDhama</h1><p class=\"text-white/50 text-2xl mb-6\" style=\"font-family:&#x27;Noto Sans Kannada&#x27;, sans-serif;opacity:0\">ಸುಧಾಮ</p><div class=\"w-12 h-px bg-white/20 mb-6 origin-center\" style=\"transform:scaleX(0)\"></div><p class=\"text-[0.6rem] tracking-[0.4em] uppercase text-white/30\" style=\"font-family:&#x27;Inter&#x27;, sans-serif;opacity:0\">Hebri · Udupi · Karnataka</p><p class=\"absolute bottom-12 text-[0.55rem] tracking-[0.4em] uppercase text-white/30\" style=\"font-family:&#x27;Inter&#x27;, sans-serif;opacity:0\">Tap to enter</p></div><div id=\"read-progress\" style=\"width:0%\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></div><a href=\"#main-content\" class=\"sr-only focus:not-sr-only focus:absolute focus:z-50 top-4 left-4 bg-white text-black p-4 rounded-lg\">Skip to main content</a><header class=\"fixed top-0 left-0 right-0 z-50 transition-all duration-500 bg-transparent\"><div class=\"max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 md:px-10 h-16 flex items-center justify-between\"><a class=\"flex-shrink-0 flex items-center gap-2.5\" href=\"/\"><div class=\"relative w-8 h-8\"><img alt=\"SuDhama\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" class=\"object-contain\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\" sizes=\"32px\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FLogo.png&amp;w=16&amp;q=75 16w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FLogo.png&amp;w=32&amp;q=75 32w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FLogo.png&amp;w=48&amp;q=75 48w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FLogo.png&amp;w=64&amp;q=75 64w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FLogo.png&amp;w=96&amp;q=75 96w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FLogo.png&amp;w=128&amp;q=75 128w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FLogo.png&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 256w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FLogo.png&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 384w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FLogo.png&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FLogo.png&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FLogo.png&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FLogo.png&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FLogo.png&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FLogo.png&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FLogo.png&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FLogo.png&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FLogo.png&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\"/></div><span class=\"font-playfair text-base font-semibold tracking-wide transition-colors duration-300 text-white\">SuDhama</span></a><nav class=\"hidden md:flex items-center gap-1\"><a class=\"font-inter text-[0.72rem] tracking-wide px-3.5 py-2 rounded-sm transition-colors duration-200 text-white/85 hover:text-white\" href=\"/#farmhouse\">The Farmhouse</a><a class=\"font-inter text-[0.72rem] tracking-wide px-3.5 py-2 rounded-sm transition-colors duration-200 text-white/85 hover:text-white\" href=\"/#farm\">Our Farm</a><a class=\"font-inter text-[0.72rem] tracking-wide px-3.5 py-2 rounded-sm transition-colors duration-200 text-white/85 hover:text-white\" href=\"/#cows\">Our Cows</a><a class=\"font-inter text-[0.72rem] tracking-wide px-3.5 py-2 rounded-sm transition-colors duration-200 text-white/85 hover:text-white\" href=\"/#story\">Our Story</a><a class=\"font-inter text-[0.72rem] tracking-wide px-3.5 py-2 rounded-sm transition-colors duration-200 text-white/85 hover:text-white\" href=\"/blog\">Sacred Journeys</a></nav><button type=\"button\" class=\"md:hidden flex flex-col justify-center gap-[5px] w-9 h-9 p-1.5\" aria-label=\"Toggle menu\" aria-expanded=\"false\"><span class=\"block h-px w-full transition-all duration-300  bg-white\"></span><span class=\"block h-px w-full transition-all duration-300  bg-white\"></span><span class=\"block h-px w-full transition-all duration-300  bg-white\"></span></button></div></header><main id=\"main-content\"><section id=\"home\" class=\"relative h-screen min-h-[600px] overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"absolute inset-0 will-change-transform\" style=\"transform:none\"><img alt=\"SuDhama farm, aerial view\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" class=\"object-cover object-center\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\" sizes=\"100vw\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FFarm.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FFarm.jpg&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FFarm.jpg&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FFarm.jpg&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FFarm.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FFarm.jpg&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FFarm.jpg&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FFarm.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FFarm.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\"/></div><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-black/20 via-black/30 to-black/70\"></div><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-black/15 via-transparent to-transparent\"></div><div class=\"relative z-10 h-full flex flex-col items-center justify-center text-center text-white px-6\" style=\"opacity:1\"><p class=\"font-inter text-[0.6rem] uppercase text-white/55 mb-5 tracking-[0.35em]\" style=\"opacity:0;letter-spacing:0.6em\">Hebri · Udupi · Karnataka</p><h1 class=\"font-playfair leading-none mb-2\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(40px)\"><span class=\"hero-title-shadow block text-6xl sm:text-7xl md:text-8xl lg:text-9xl font-bold\">SuDhama</span><span class=\"font-kannada block text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-light text-white/65 mt-2\">ಸುಧಾಮ</span></h1><div class=\"w-14 h-px bg-white/35 my-6 origin-center\" style=\"transform:scaleX(0)\"></div><p class=\"font-inter max-w-md text-white/65 text-sm md:text-base leading-relaxed font-light\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(16px)\">A sanctuary in the heart of Udupi — organic land, heritage cows, and the slow life lived with intention.</p><div class=\"mt-8 flex flex-wrap gap-3 justify-center\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(12px)\"><a class=\"font-inter px-7 py-3 bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm border border-white/25 text-white text-xs tracking-widest uppercase hover:bg-white hover:text-stone-900 transition-all duration-400 rounded-sm\" href=\"/#home-features\">Explore</a><a class=\"font-inter px-7 py-3 text-white/60 text-xs tracking-widest uppercase hover:text-white transition-colors rounded-sm\" href=\"/blog\">Sacred Journeys</a></div></div><div class=\"absolute bottom-8 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2\" style=\"opacity:0\"><div class=\"w-px h-10 bg-gradient-to-b from-white/50 to-transparent\"></div></div></section><section id=\"home-features\" class=\"bg-[#FDFBF7] py-20 md:py-28\"><div class=\"max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 md:px-10\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-4 mb-14\" style=\"opacity:0\"><div class=\"h-px flex-1 bg-stone-200\"></div><span class=\"font-inter text-[0.6rem] tracking-[0.35em] uppercase text-stone-400\">What we are</span><div class=\"h-px flex-1 bg-stone-200\"></div></div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 md:gap-6\"><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)\"><a class=\"group block\" href=\"/#farmhouse\"><div class=\"relative h-56 overflow-hidden rounded-lg mb-5\"><img alt=\"SuDhama farmhouse\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" class=\"object-cover transition-transform duration-700 group-hover:scale-[1.05]\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 33vw\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FFarmhouse%20V1.jpg&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 256w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FFarmhouse%20V1.jpg&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 384w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FFarmhouse%20V1.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FFarmhouse%20V1.jpg&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FFarmhouse%20V1.jpg&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FFarmhouse%20V1.jpg&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FFarmhouse%20V1.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FFarmhouse%20V1.jpg&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FFarmhouse%20V1.jpg&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FFarmhouse%20V1.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FFarmhouse%20V1.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\"/><span class=\"font-inter absolute top-3 right-3 text-[0.6rem] text-white/60 tracking-widest\">01</span></div><h3 class=\"font-playfair text-lg text-stone-800 mb-1.5 group-hover:text-terracotta transition-colors duration-300\">The Farmhouse</h3><p class=\"font-inter text-stone-500 text-[0.8rem] leading-relaxed mb-3\">Laterite stone, clay tiles, natural cross-ventilation. Built from the land to belong to it.</p><span class=\"font-inter text-[0.65rem] text-amber-800 tracking-[0.2em] uppercase flex items-center gap-1.5\">Discover<span class=\"group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform inline-block\">→</span></span></a></div><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)\"><a class=\"group block\" href=\"/#farm\"><div class=\"relative h-56 overflow-hidden rounded-lg mb-5\"><img alt=\"The grove\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" class=\"object-cover transition-transform duration-700 group-hover:scale-[1.05]\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 33vw\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FFarm.jpg&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 256w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FFarm.jpg&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 384w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FFarm.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FFarm.jpg&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FFarm.jpg&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FFarm.jpg&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FFarm.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FFarm.jpg&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FFarm.jpg&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FFarm.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FFarm.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\"/><span class=\"font-inter absolute top-3 right-3 text-[0.6rem] text-white/60 tracking-widest\">02</span></div><h3 class=\"font-playfair text-lg text-stone-800 mb-1.5 group-hover:text-terracotta transition-colors duration-300\">The Land</h3><p class=\"font-inter text-stone-500 text-[0.8rem] leading-relaxed mb-3\">Forty acres of organic polyculture — coconut, arecanut, and rare tropical fruit grown without chemicals.</p><span class=\"font-inter text-[0.65rem] text-amber-800 tracking-[0.2em] uppercase flex items-center gap-1.5\">Discover<span class=\"group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform inline-block\">→</span></span></a></div><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)\"><a class=\"group block\" href=\"/#cows\"><div class=\"relative h-56 overflow-hidden rounded-lg mb-5\"><img alt=\"Desi cow\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" class=\"object-cover transition-transform duration-700 group-hover:scale-[1.05]\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 33vw\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FCow.jpg&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 256w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FCow.jpg&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 384w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FCow.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FCow.jpg&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FCow.jpg&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FCow.jpg&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FCow.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FCow.jpg&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FCow.jpg&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FCow.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FCow.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\"/><span class=\"font-inter absolute top-3 right-3 text-[0.6rem] text-white/60 tracking-widest\">03</span></div><h3 class=\"font-playfair text-lg text-stone-800 mb-1.5 group-hover:text-terracotta transition-colors duration-300\">The Cows</h3><p class=\"font-inter text-stone-500 text-[0.8rem] leading-relaxed mb-3\">Indigenous Gir cows, free-roaming and revered. Ahimsa dairy — A2 milk on their terms alone.</p><span class=\"font-inter text-[0.65rem] text-amber-800 tracking-[0.2em] uppercase flex items-center gap-1.5\">Discover<span class=\"group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform inline-block\">→</span></span></a></div></div></div></section><section id=\"farmhouse\" class=\"py-20 md:py-28 border-t border-stone-100\"><div class=\"max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 md:px-10\"><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 md:gap-20 items-center\"><div class=\"space-y-5\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateX(-24px)\"><span class=\"font-inter label-eyebrow\">A Place to Stay</span><h2 class=\"font-playfair text-3xl md:text-4xl text-stone-900 leading-tight\">A Home Built<br/><span class=\"text-terracotta\">from the Land</span></h2><p class=\"font-inter text-stone-600 leading-relaxed text-sm\">Built with locally sourced Laterite stone, the farmhouse embodies zero-mile construction. Natural cross-ventilation and traditional clay tiles create a space that breathes with the land.</p><p class=\"font-inter text-stone-400 leading-relaxed text-sm\">The stone darkens with rain and lightens in sun. The roof tiles gather moss at their edges. Nothing here fights nature.</p><div class=\"flex gap-8 pt-2 border-t border-stone-100\"><div><p class=\"font-playfair text-stone-800 font-semibold text-sm\">Laterite Stone</p><p class=\"font-inter text-[0.6rem] text-stone-400 tracking-widest uppercase mt-0.5\">Material</p></div><div><p class=\"font-playfair text-stone-800 font-semibold text-sm\">Zero-mile</p><p class=\"font-inter text-[0.6rem] text-stone-400 tracking-widest uppercase mt-0.5\">Build</p></div><div><p class=\"font-playfair text-stone-800 font-semibold text-sm\">Passive cooling</p><p class=\"font-inter text-[0.6rem] text-stone-400 tracking-widest uppercase mt-0.5\">Climate</p></div></div></div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-2 gap-3\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateX(24px)\"><div class=\"relative col-span-2 h-60 rounded-xl overflow-hidden\"><img alt=\"SuDhama farmhouse\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" class=\"object-cover\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\" sizes=\"50vw\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FFarmhouse.jpg&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 384w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FFarmhouse.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FFarmhouse.jpg&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FFarmhouse.jpg&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FFarmhouse.jpg&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FFarmhouse.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FFarmhouse.jpg&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FFarmhouse.jpg&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FFarmhouse.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FFarmhouse.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\"/></div><div class=\"relative h-36 rounded-xl overflow-hidden\"><img alt=\"Front view\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" class=\"object-cover\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\" sizes=\"25vw\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FFarmhouse%20V1.jpg&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 256w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FFarmhouse%20V1.jpg&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 384w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FFarmhouse%20V1.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FFarmhouse%20V1.jpg&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FFarmhouse%20V1.jpg&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FFarmhouse%20V1.jpg&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FFarmhouse%20V1.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FFarmhouse%20V1.jpg&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FFarmhouse%20V1.jpg&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FFarmhouse%20V1.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FFarmhouse%20V1.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\"/></div><div class=\"relative h-36 rounded-xl overflow-hidden\"><img alt=\"Laterite stone detail\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" class=\"object-cover\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\" sizes=\"25vw\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FlatHome.jpg&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 256w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FlatHome.jpg&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 384w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FlatHome.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FlatHome.jpg&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FlatHome.jpg&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FlatHome.jpg&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FlatHome.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FlatHome.jpg&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FlatHome.jpg&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FlatHome.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FlatHome.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\"/></div></div></div></div></section><section id=\"farm\" class=\"py-20 md:py-28 bg-stone-900 text-stone-100\"><div class=\"max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 md:px-10\"><div class=\"flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-end md:justify-between gap-4 mb-14\"><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><span class=\"font-inter text-[0.6rem] tracking-[0.35em] uppercase text-amber-600 mb-3 block\">What the Land Gives</span><h2 class=\"font-playfair text-3xl md:text-4xl text-stone-100 leading-tight\">Our Plantations</h2></div><p class=\"font-inter text-stone-500 text-sm max-w-xs leading-relaxed\" style=\"opacity:0\">No pesticides. No synthetic inputs.<br class=\"hidden md:block\"/>Everything grown by hand, in season.</p></div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-4 md:grid-cols-8 gap-2 md:gap-3\"><div class=\"group\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(12px)\"><div class=\"relative aspect-square rounded-lg overflow-hidden mb-1.5\"><img alt=\"Mangoes\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" class=\"object-cover transition-transform duration-500 group-hover:scale-110\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\" sizes=\"12vw\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FMango.png&amp;w=96&amp;q=75 96w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FMango.png&amp;w=128&amp;q=75 128w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FMango.png&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 256w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FMango.png&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 384w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FMango.png&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FMango.png&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FMango.png&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FMango.png&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FMango.png&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FMango.png&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FMango.png&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FMango.png&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FMango.png&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\"/><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-black/25 group-hover:bg-black/10 transition-colors\"></div></div><p class=\"font-inter text-[0.65rem] font-medium text-stone-300 leading-tight text-center\">Mangoes</p><p class=\"font-inter text-[0.55rem] text-stone-600 text-center\">May–Jun</p></div><div class=\"group\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(12px)\"><div class=\"relative aspect-square rounded-lg overflow-hidden mb-1.5\"><img alt=\"Bananas\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" class=\"object-cover transition-transform duration-500 group-hover:scale-110\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\" sizes=\"12vw\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FBanana.jpg&amp;w=96&amp;q=75 96w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FBanana.jpg&amp;w=128&amp;q=75 128w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FBanana.jpg&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 256w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FBanana.jpg&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 384w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FBanana.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FBanana.jpg&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FBanana.jpg&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FBanana.jpg&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FBanana.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FBanana.jpg&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FBanana.jpg&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FBanana.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FBanana.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\"/><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-black/25 group-hover:bg-black/10 transition-colors\"></div></div><p class=\"font-inter text-[0.65rem] font-medium text-stone-300 leading-tight text-center\">Bananas</p><p class=\"font-inter text-[0.55rem] text-stone-600 text-center\">Year-round</p></div><div class=\"group\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(12px)\"><div class=\"relative aspect-square rounded-lg overflow-hidden mb-1.5\"><img alt=\"Jackfruit\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" class=\"object-cover transition-transform duration-500 group-hover:scale-110\" style=\"position:absolute